    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you gain the ability to twist your powers to suit your needs. You gain two of the following Metamagic options of your choice. You gain another one at 10th and 17th level.&nbsp;You can use only one Metamagic option on a power when you cast it, unless otherwise noted.</p>\n        <p><a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sw5e.classfeatures\" data-id=\"zElYrOcCFFMhB6Xl\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Careful Power</a></p>\n        <p><a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sw5e.classfeatures\" data-id=\"DZpAa3LzMNBexbmX\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Distant Power</a></p>\n        <p><a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sw5e.classfeatures\" data-id=\"IWpe0Y9uAStHGiH1\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Empowered Power</a></p>\n        <p><a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sw5e.classfeatures\" data-id=\"tQxlKyAx9sgPrbgj\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Extended Power</a></p>\n        <p><a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sw5e.classfeatures\" data-id=\"tNG2qi9zhmXEkecA\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Heightened Power</a></p>\n        <p><a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sw5e.classfeatures\" data-id=\"nViGf6bZ6DQAJhkw\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Quickened Power</a></p>\n        <p><a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sw5e.classfeatures\" data-id=\"fXa0DMhoVLtbBu9l\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Subtle Power</a></p>\n        <p><a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sw5e.classfeatures\" data-id=\"Qb391hakCfmH4w8p\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Twinned Power</a></p>\n        <p>You can drag your choices from the above onto your character sheet and it will automatically update.</p>",
